{"tid":464774,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"嚴正聲明，今日係國殤紀念日，絕對唔係乜撚野光棍節、購物日","createTime":"2017-11-11T00:55:36.000Z","updateTime":"2017-11-12T02:26:06.000Z","uid":66260,"like":67,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"d6ac3a2681b745cfe9cff73ebde8eb00b8d6e9ae","tid":464774,"uid":66260,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-11T00:55:36.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://zh.m.wikipedia.org/zh-tw/國殤紀念日\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fzh.m.wikipedia.org%2Fzh-tw%2F%E5%9C%8B%E6%AE%A4%E7%B4%80%E5%BF%B5%E6%97%A5&d=4y26Nzl7bms%2FR0TUX1plygHuyxefasl%2FZxVLfhQSBMM%3D&h=cff9b268\" target=\"_blank\">https://zh.m.wikipedia.org/zh-tw/國殤紀念日</a><br />\n國殤紀念日（英語：Remembrance Day）訂立於每年的11月11日，為一個紀念在第一次世界大戰、第二次世界大戰和其他戰爭中犧牲的軍人與平民的紀念節日，又譯「和平紀念日」、「陣亡將士紀念日」。<br />\n<br />\n見到一個二個係咁話今日網購好抵乜乜乜，睇見都想嘔<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">毋忘當年為港捐軀既英國士兵<br />\n拒絕支那劣質文化，你我有責</span></span>"},{"pid":"99a0e11f541a68f923bae65502d91bd3a75a26a1","tid":464774,"uid":66260,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-11T00:58:19.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">Lest we forget</span><br />\n<img src=\"https://i.ytimg.com/vi/OsMwmv06cE0/maxresdefault.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.ytimg.com%2Fvi%2FOsMwmv06cE0%2Fmaxresdefault.jpg&h=649fd553&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"7b6ef634c4e655ff79fd0a7859767402ddd0282e","tid":464774,"uid":8048,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-11T00:58:23.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fed82b417d893b9f78235c9d4715014e5655a558","tid":464774,"uid":79563,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-11T01:00:49.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>毋忘當年為港捐軀既英國士兵</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n二戰時, 除左英國士兵, 仲有蘇格蘭、加拿大、印度、香港義勇軍戰死<br />\n<br />\n一戰時, 就有數千香港人受僱, 去法國修工事後勤野, 都有死人"},{"pid":"df12fc086dbc15b313f092ef99a44140baffe2be","tid":464774,"uid":54959,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-11T01:02:06.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"412c99a9374768922fcc42f9d668f50d7e497843","tid":464774,"uid":66260,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-11T01:02:28.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>毋忘當年為港捐軀既英國士兵</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n二戰時, 除左英國士兵, 仲有蘇格蘭、加拿大、印度、香港義勇軍戰死<br />\n<br />\n一戰時, 就有數千香港人受僱, 去法國修工事後勤野, 都有死人</blockquote><br />\n感謝補充<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"46aa71d5434cf66349de17ac3ba79ec686a44cc3","tid":464774,"uid":9348,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-11T01:04:45.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>Watershed Hong Kong<br />\n<br />\n#PoppyDay 明天早上，我們約15名義工，會於中環、銅鑼灣、山頂等位置及於不同崗位義賣紅花，請大家多多支持一年一度的Poppy Day，為香港退伍軍人籌款。<br />\n<br />\nSupport local ex-servicemen, women and their dependants by buying poppies tomorrow morning on the streets of HK Island from 9am to 12:15pm.<br />\n<br />\nPoppy Day is the Flag Day (to be held on second Saturday in November every year) of The Royal British Legion Hong Kong &amp; China Branch and is the only day during the year that the Legion raises funds from the public.<br />\n<br />\n#LestWeForget<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/11/11/081319_f64dfb6819bc72ed017467fa49b674c5.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F11%2F11%2F081319_f64dfb6819bc72ed017467fa49b674c5.jpg&h=0eb517d6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/WatershedHK/posts/551781988489907\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2FWatershedHK%2Fposts%2F551781988489907&d=4y26Nzl7bms%2FR0TUX1plygHuyxefasl%2FZxVLfhQSBMM%3D&h=71f41308\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/WatershedHK/posts/551781988489907</a></blockquote><br />\nin case今日唔係香港島搵食可以參考this link<br />\n<a href=\"http://branches.britishlegion.org.uk/branches/hong-kong/poppy-appeal\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fbranches.britishlegion.org.uk%2Fbranches%2Fhong-kong%2Fpoppy-appeal&d=4y26Nzl7bms%2FR0TUX1plygHuyxefasl%2FZxVLfhQSBMM%3D&h=5b41c461\" target=\"_blank\">http://branches.britishlegion.org.uk/branches/hong-kong/poppy-appeal</a></blockquote>"},{"pid":"effb8fcd75501d002ec6d51b62993800853d3850","tid":464774,"uid":99291,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-11T01:19:00.000Z","msg":"感謝！"},{"pid":"22ef548d056d1fdee143720facd89b50035824f4","tid":464774,"uid":105995,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-11T06:31:04.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fce22dd349e94df503cae770f0dea9686d3f2ad2","tid":464774,"uid":27909,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-11T06:36:37.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"aaf202ba3a2ae9eb3f306a771dd684fd19f3c3a7","tid":464774,"uid":11753,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-11T07:10:08.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"289033f6c05a11e55ed98ec00d4bb8971537d7ff","tid":464774,"uid":128603,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-11T07:18:14.000Z","msg":"講得好<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"66330bc14defc88c70d9fcc4c80c92f0e3bd2883","tid":464774,"uid":56999,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-11T07:20:01.000Z","msg":"但係都殺支那畜牲<br />\n<br />\n呢部份<br />\n咁應該慶祝"},{"pid":"8f75b18d4a5b6bd0e14aa7737232a51f6d81a00b","tid":464774,"uid":48234,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-11T12:41:45.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/6c4PUfy.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2F6c4PUfy.gif&h=bf323894&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"3772cd63f3578ed5bd4c440de12d35458cd7747f","tid":464774,"uid":67225,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-11T12:42:22.000Z","msg":"香港的和平紀念日原先是每年11月11日（1919年開始），紀念第一次世界大戰結束重歸和平，1945年香港重光後改為11月的第二個星期日（又稱Remembrance Sunday Day）。香港總督和政府官員會在中環和平紀念碑紀念第一次世界大戰和悼念陣亡戰士。"},{"pid":"0d88b74c877a324138f4fa8c7882e4b277a605d4","tid":464774,"uid":67225,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-12T02:26:06.000Z","msg":"1945年香港重光後改為11月的第二個星期日"}]}